title: Soho - Hippychick - 1990 Electronic Dance
description:
[i]Wow. This is a time machine traveling you back 25 years. This song was hugely popular but as far as Big Papi can see gets absolutely zero airplay these days. If you were in the clubs during that time you will go "Ahhhhhhhh I love this song!!!"

Oh crap it fades into the next track so this song ends rather abruptly!!!. The entire CD will be upped tomorrow so check back then. If you want this as a stand-alone single you'll need the radio version or will need to fade this one out yourself.

The CD is not bad.....not bad at all...

- Big Papi[/i]
